<project xml:id="cool-comoDecidirias" xmlns:xi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XInclude"> 

<title>¿Cómo decidirías?</title>

<statement>
  <p>¿Cómo harías para decidir si <m>\frac{6}{4}</m> es equivalente a <m>\frac{3}{4}</m>? Explica o muestra cómo razonaste.</p>
</statement>

<solution>
    <p>[+++++++++++++++]</p>
    <p>Sample responses:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>I know <m>\frac{6}{4}</m> is not equivalent to <m>\frac{3}{4}</m> because they are not in the same location on the number line.</li>
      <li>I know <m>\frac{6}{4}</m> is not equivalent to <m>\frac{3}{4}</m> because they aren't the same size.</li>
      <li>I know <m>\frac{6}{4}</m> is not equivalent to <m>\frac{3}{4}</m> because it means 6 fourths, which is more than 3 fourths.</li>
    </ul>
  </solution>


